		<li id="comment-3128">
<div class="clearfix"><div class="avatarholder"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/99b9251a5f566fe48215d28a4da2f91b?s=32&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ahousebythepark.com%2Fjournal%2Fwp-content%2Fthemes%2FHouse%2Fimages%2Fgravatar_default.gif%3Fs%3D32&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' /></div>			<div class="commentauthor"><a href='http://www.bluetickdig.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Alexis GallisÃ¡</a> says:</div></div>
			
